leve.name: Twenty-nine Was the Cutoff
leve.description: The 426th Order mendicant Zi Gu has slain thirty men and women of the Maelstrom; by the laws of the sea and man his life is forfeit. He thinks to hide in Bloodshore, which has a reputation─outdated, we can assure you─for being friendly to both outlaws and alchemy. In the name of the Maelstrom, carry out his sentence.
